Package: libao0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: libasound1
Description: Cross Platform Audio Output Library
 Libao is a cross platform audio output library.  It currently supports
 ESD, OSS, Solaris, and IRIX.
